<item>
            <title>[LU-8451] assert if cpu_pattern specifies exactly one cpu in the partition</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8451</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;cpu_pattern can sepcify exactly 1 cpu in a partition:&lt;br/&gt;
&quot;0&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&quot;. That means CPT0 will have CPU 0.  CPU 0 can have&lt;br/&gt;
hyperthreading enabled. This combination would result in&lt;br/&gt;
weight = cfs_cpu_ht_nsiblings(0);&lt;br/&gt;
hrp-&amp;gt;hrp_nthrs = cfs_cpt_weight(ptlrpc_hr.hr_cpt_table, i);&lt;br/&gt;
hrp-&amp;gt;hrp_nthrs /= weight;&lt;br/&gt;
evaluating to 0 &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Causing LASSERT(hrp-&amp;gt;hrp_nthrs &amp;gt; 0); to trigger&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Patch&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/19106/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/19106/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;attempts to resolve this issue.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
